title: Urbanization in Japan 2018
summary: In general Share of urban population has stayed the same over the Year.
Share of urban population is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2016.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Share of urban population, about 91.46 was reported at Year 2016
The lowest Share of urban population, of value 91.3 was reported at Year 2014
